<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/516904-is-this-told-with-a-similar-narrative">Is this told with a similar narrative style as In Cold Blood by Truman Capote??? If so, I&#39;m definitely down to read it!</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_516904'><a id="like_count_community_question_516904" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/516904?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">1 like</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F5345.The_Innocent_Man">like</a></span>

</li>
