<li class='cover' id='bookCover_80101'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/80101.The_Dreams_of_Ada"><img alt="The Dreams of Ada" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1386924495l/80101._SX98_.jpg" />
